longBusinessSummary: Flame Seal Products, Inc. develops fire prevention technologies in the United States. It offers fire retardant coatings, as well as fabric fire, leather fire, paper fire, wood fire, and wildfire retardants. Flame Seal Products, Inc. was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Houston, Texas.
